OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fa few light showers possible during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Largely dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells developing overnight, although
OL,9,Fwith a few isolated coastal showers
OL,10,Flikely. Feeling cool with a patchy
OL,11,Ffrost developing in some prone rural
OL,12,Fspots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAfter a chilly start, sunny
OL,15,Fspells develop through the day.
OL,16,FLargely dry, cooler than recent days,
OL,17,Fwith occasional coastal showers
OL,18,Fpossible. Light winds, with a frosty
OL,19,Fnight to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
