OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday brings sunny spells and the
OL,7,Fodd shower. Conditions turn more
OL,8,Funsettled Friday and Saturday with
OL,9,Fspells of rain or showers,
OL,10,Foccasionally heavy. At times cool,
OL,11,Fwith isolated frosts overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
